&quot; style=&quot;color:#fff;&quot; class=&quot;twitter-post-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Twitter Post</a>
<blockquote><a href="https://www.alaraby.co.uk/home/%3Cblockquote%20class=" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank"><br/>— CiLuna (@CiLuna27) </a><a href="https://twitter.com/CiLuna27/status/1152713866767458305?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank">July 20, 2019</a></blockquote>

